1.1.28.Notes:
Note: v1.1.26-27 is gone.
Version 1.1.28 of xmoj-script ships a lot of quality of life improvements and bug fixes. 

- Add spell checking for bbs and short_msg
- Fix the problem status page
- Make the upload_std interface prettier
- Use the same parameter as xmoj for the native link
- Sleep for a second after submitting to prevent xmoj from crashing
- Update support link 
 <big>Please note that upload_std now uploads the user's code if there is no std.
 See you in the next release!🎆</big>
